Package: treeExtension
Type: Package
Title: Tree Rooting, Monophyly Checks, and Node-Level BLAST Summaries
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R:
    person("Chen", "Yanpeng", email = "yanpengch@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight utilities for working with rooted phylogenetic trees,
    IQ-TREE outputs, and BLAST tabular results. Includes tools to rebuild a
    rooted binary tree from an outgroup branch, assess monophyly at a
    user-specified taxonomic rank, build phylum-level constraint trees, and
    summarize BLASTN pairwise similarity statistics across internal tree nodes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    ape,
    ggtree,
    readr,
    tibble,
    tidytree,
    treeio
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
